		{
			dependencies: ["3811F52536EF179D"]
			description: [
				"&5&lAge VIII Â· Ascension.&r"
				""
				"You have stood at the edge of the solar system. Only now does the summit open."
				""
				"Everything you built - the sieve, the forge, the reactors, the army, the fleet - converges on one craft that ends the world you started on. The road is long and every step is here: bridge fluorite, claim the Twilight's fire, spin fissile fuel, run a fission reactor, condense antimatter, gather the relics of the fallen, and forge the Heart."
			]
			icon: "skyforge:heart_of_the_sky"
			id: "2106000000000001"
			rewards: [{ id: "2106000000000101", type: "xp_levels", xp_levels: 5 }]
			shape: "hexagon"
			size: 1.5d
			subtitle: "&7The final climb"
			tasks: [{ id: "2106000000000201", title: "Begin the ascent", type: "checkmark" }]
			title: "&5Age VIII Â· Ascension"
			x: -10.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: [
				"2106000000000001"
				"10583B7DED57F345"
			]
			description: [
				"&cThe fission gate.&r In this pack, every batch of Fission Reactor Casings is forged around a &eFiery Ingot&r - Twilight Forest metal, smelted from iron and the Hydra's blood (or the Ur-Ghast's tears)."
				""
				"No Twilight conquest, no reactor. Stock four ingots and the atom is yours to split."
			]
			icon: "twilightforest:fiery_ingot"
			id: "2106000000000010"
			rewards: [{ count: 2, id: "2106000000000110", item: "twilightforest:fiery_ingot", type: "item" }]
			shape: "diamond"
			subtitle: "&7The Twilight's toll"
			tasks: [{ count: 4L, id: "2106000000000230", item: "twilightforest:fiery_ingot", type: "item" }]
			title: "&5Trial of Fire"
			x: -8.0d
			y: -1.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["2106000000000001"]
			description: [
				"Mekanism's fission fuel needs &eFluorite&r - and like every ore in this pack, none of it spawns in the void."
				""
				"The keystone bridge covers it: &7Keystone + 2 Sky Dust&r &8â†’&r 4 Fluorite. Fluorite feeds the Hydrofluoric Acid that turns uranium into fissile fuel. Without it, nothing below is possible - so start here."
			]
			icon: "mekanism:fluorite_gem"
			id: "2106000000000008"
			rewards: [{ count: 4, id: "2106000000000108", item: "mekanism:fluorite_gem", type: "item" }]
			shape: "diamond"
			subtitle: "&7The missing piece of the fuel line"
			tasks: [{ count: 4L, id: "2106000000000208", item: "mekanism:fluorite_gem", type: "item" }]
			title: "&5Bridge Fluorite"
			x: -8.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["2106000000000008"]
			description: [
				"Fissile Fuel is a chain: sieve &ecrushed deepslate&r for Uranium Ore Chunks, smelt them, and refine into &eYellowcake Uranium&r."
				""
				"Then an &eIsotopic Centrifuge&r spins Uranium Hexafluoride (made from your fluorite's Hydrofluoric Acid) into Fissile Fuel - the gas the reactor burns. Build the centrifuge and stockpile yellowcake."
			]
			icon: "mekanism:yellow_cake_uranium"
			id: "2106000000000009"
			rewards: [{ id: "2106000000000109", type: "xp_levels", xp_levels: 3 }]
			shape: "gear"
			subtitle: "&7Uranium into fissile fuel"
			tasks: [
				{ count: 4L, id: "2106000000000209", item: "mekanism:yellow_cake_uranium", type: "item" }
				{ id: "2106000000000219", item: "mekanism:isotopic_centrifuge", type: "item" }
			]
			title: "&5The Fuel Line"
			x: -6.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: [
				"2106000000000009"
				"2106000000000010"
			]
			description: [
				"Now build the reactor itself - a sealed multiblock of casings, a fuel assembly to hold the fissile fuel, a control rod to throttle it, and a port to pipe coolant in and steam out."
				""
				"&eEvery casing batch takes a Fiery Ingot&r - the Twilight's toll, paid in full."
				""
				"&cRun it carefully.&r An unmanaged fission reactor melts down and takes your island with it. Sodium or water cooling, and never let the temperature run away."
			]
			icon: "mekanismgenerators:fission_reactor_casing"
			id: "2106000000000002"
			rewards: [{ id: "2106000000000102", type: "xp_levels", xp_levels: 5 }]
			shape: "gear"
			size: 1.25d
			subtitle: "&7Split the atom"
			tasks: [
				{ count: 4L, id: "2106000000000202", item: "mekanismgenerators:fission_reactor_casing", type: "item" }
				{ id: "2106000000000212", item: "mekanismgenerators:fission_fuel_assembly", type: "item" }
				{ id: "2106000000000222", item: "mekanismgenerators:control_rod_assembly", type: "item" }
				{ id: "2106000000000232", item: "mekanismgenerators:fission_reactor_port", type: "item" }
			]
			title: "&5Go Fission"
			x: -4.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["2106000000000002"]
			description: [
				"A fission reactor makes heat, not power - it boils coolant into &esteam&r, and steam is useless until something eats it."
				""
				"Build an &eIndustrial Turbine&r: casing, rotor, vents, a rotational complex and coils. It swallows the reactor's steam and returns a torrent of Forge Energy. This is what actually powers the SPS."
			]
			icon: "mekanismgenerators:turbine_rotor"
			id: "210600000000000A"
			rewards: [{ id: "210600000000010A", type: "xp_levels", xp_levels: 5 }]
			shape: "gear"
			subtitle: "&7Turn steam into power"
			tasks: [
				{ count: 4L, id: "210600000000020A", item: "mekanismgenerators:turbine_casing", type: "item" }
				{ id: "210600000000021A", item: "mekanismgenerators:turbine_rotor", type: "item" }
